@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hezpfc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos((0.29 / v2))
    tmp = (((v2 + 0.14 - v2 + 0.90) / 0.41) * (v1 - 0.54))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs((tmp + 0.37 - v0 + 0.20)))
    data[tid] = v0
